package.name: tim-jetty-6.1.4
package.description: The Terracotta Integration Module for Jetty provides the basic features of Terracotta Distributed Shared Objects (DSO) as well as web-application session state clustering.

contents.readme:
Copy this TIM into $TC_HOME/modules and add the following to your tc-config.xml:
<clients> <modules> <module group-id="org.mortbay.jetty" name="tim-jetty-6.1.4" version="1.1.0"/> </modules> </clients>

package.name: tim-terracotta-cache
package.description: Drop-in replacement for JBoss TreeCache and PojoCache powered by Terracotta. This is a Terracotta Integration Module (TIM) for Terracotta Cache, a distributed cache that is API-compatible with the JBoss PojoCache and TreeCache components. If you are currently using one of these components, you can replace the use of those components with Terracotta Cache and only minimal code changes.
